    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Implements comprising wheels, usually of metal or wood, having a decorative or fluted edge and mounted on a handle, used to impress decorative edges or designs in a soft surface, such as dough or clay.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
